    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment is accepted at assurance level Low. Seven of thirteen credibility factors were assessed; three factors (numerical solver error, use error, equivalency of input parameters) were not assessed and deferred as beyond scope. The assessed factors demonstrate partial compliance with MRL 3 requirements. The unassessed factors were not formally evaluated against MRL 3 criteria, representing an epistemic gap. The decision team accepted the package based on the assessed factors meeting minimum thresholds for the intended low-assurance submission, with the expectation that unassessed factors will be addressed prior to pivotal submission.",
